OL,3,CBirmingham City Council remains
OL,4,Cwithout new leader amid ongoing
OL,5,Ccoalition talks
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council remains
OL,8,Fwithout a new leader after councillors
OL,9,Fmet for the first full council session
OL,10,Fsince the local elections, with no
OL,11,Fagreement yet in place to form an
OL,12,Fadministration.
OL,14,FCoalition talks between the Green
OL,15,FParty and Liberal Democrats are said
OL,16,Fto be "going well", but insiders say
OL,17,Fthere hasn't been enough time to reach
OL,18,Fa formal agreement since Labour ruled
OL,19,Fitself out of any power-sharing
OL,20,Farrangement on Friday.
OL,26,@xD@GOUxD@RO]
