OL,3,CBirmingham City Council remains
OL,4,Cwithout new leader amid ongoing
OL,5,Ccoalition talks
OL,7,FToday's full council meeting of 101
OL,8,Fcouncillors was adjourned until
OL,9,Ffurther notice.
OL,11,FThe authority remains in a period of
OL,12,Funcertainty, almost two weeks after
OL,13,Fvoters went to the polls, with no
OL,14,Fclear administration confirmed.
OL,16,FUnite the Union has called for a swift
OL,17,Fagreement between councillors, so the
OL,18,Fbin-strike deal agreed with Labour
OL,19,Fbefore the election can be concluded,
OL,20,Fallowing striking workers to return to
OL,21,Fwork.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
