OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779307554
OL,3,CBirmingham City Council remains
OL,4,Cwithout new leader amid ongoing
OL,5,Ccoalition talks
OL,7,FReform UK councillors ruled themselves
OL,8,Fout of joining any governing
OL,9,Fcoalition. Despite being the largest
OL,10,Fparty with 23 councillors, the party
OL,11,Fsaid it had "no viable route" to
OL,12,Fforming an administration.
OL,14,FOn Friday, Labour also ruled itself
OL,15,Fout, significantly narrowing the
OL,16,Fpotential routes to a majority
OL,17,Fadministration.
OL,26,@sD@MOUsD@]O]
