PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779307554
OL,3,CBirmingham City Council remains
OL,4,Cwithout new leader amid ongoing
OL,5,Ccoalition talks
OL,7,FHolding 17 seats, the new Labour group
OL,8,Fleader, Councillor Nicky Brennan, said
OL,9,Fthe party would not enter any
OL,10,Fcoalition or power-sharing arrangement
OL,11,Fwith other groups.
OL,13,FThe Greens hold 19 councillors and the
OL,14,FLiberal Democrats 12, leaving them
OL,15,Fwell short of the 51 seats needed for
OL,16,Fa majority.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
