PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779307554
OL,3,CBirmingham City Council remains
OL,4,Cwithout new leader amid ongoing
OL,5,Ccoalition talks
OL,7,FThe Conservative Party, with 16 seats,
OL,8,Falso appeared to rule itself out of
OL,9,Fcoalition talks, with one senior
OL,10,Ffigure warning that "any coalition
OL,11,Fthat tries to govern from the extremes
OL,12,Fwill fail."
OL,14,FThere is also political sensitivity
OL,15,Faround coalition-building after events
OL,16,Fin Worcestershire, where a proposed
OL,17,Farrangement involving Conservatives
OL,18,Fand Greens quickly collapsed and led
OL,19,Fto disciplinary action within the
OL,20,FConservative Party.
OL,26,@rD@UOUtD@KO]
