PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779307554
OL,3,CBirmingham City Council remains
OL,4,Cwithout new leader amid ongoing
OL,5,Ccoalition talks
OL,7,FThe Greens, as the second-largest
OL,8,Fgroup on the council, are expected to
OL,9,Fplay a central role in any future
OL,10,Fadministration. However, the numbers
OL,11,Fsuggest a minority or cross-party
OL,12,Farrangement may ultimately be required.
OL,14,FThe position of independent
OL,15,Fcouncillors remains unclear, and their
OL,16,Fsupport could prove decisive in any
OL,17,Ffuture vote to appoint a leader.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
